"Ignorance is strength" is the second full length album from swedish melodic death veterans Taketh. With this release the band is taking a step away from tradition with a full Creative Commons release, enabling free sharing, remixing and derivative works.
Taketh presents a raw and unfiltered sound bringing back memories of the old days of the gothenburg sound. The perfect fit for fans of Dark Tranquillity, At the Gates and the old In Flames.
